N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 60.9 - Reporting requirements

State Regulations

Accredited veterinarians shall immediately notify the
department in writing of any positive test results to any deer tuberculosis
test performed by that veterinarian. Notes
